MusicBrainz Data Chunks
-----------------------
This folder contains chunks of data downloaded from the musicbrainz archive for the music map.
Releases are tracked in each csv split by their decade of release to reduce load time
Releases are also split between two files for each decade- _music and _meta, where music contains only basic information : lat/long, release year, and genres
Meta files contain the complex release information at the same row for each _music file : mbid, release year, artist, release name, genres
Genres in the _music files are stored in a compressed manner where each genre searched is converted to a number stored in a dictionary file.
